.planning/review/REVIEW-codex.err:597:**Why explicit peak list for centroid?** Reference writer's peaks facet only recognizes canonical `CentroidPeak` schema (m/z f64 + intensity f32 per mzpeaks crate). Raw arrays with dtype-suffixed names (`mz_f64`/`intensity_f32`) don't map into peaks facet, so values serialize as NULL without the peak list.
