The line-level pass supports the fixes: nullable staging is in `ScanStager`, nullable leaf emission is centralized in `MzPeakColumns`, and the metadata builder emits the added spectrum/scan fields in the same order as the reference schema. I’m checking tests added around these behaviors and whether a local test run is possible without writes.
