codex
The same footer-count problem exists on `spectra_metadata.parquet`: the reference carries a nonzero `spectrum_data_point_count`, while the current metadata builder hard-codes `"0"`. Even if data facets themselves carry real counts, these metadata footers are stale and validator-visible.
